title: Military in Scale - Magazine Pack [1994-2007]
description:
This magazine is closed since 2012. 


Military In Scale was established in December 1992. It is no longer a monthly magazine. Up to 4 special issues per year will be released which will contain even more Military Modelling including. Armour, Aircraft and a full range of dioramas.

With a wide scope of subjects and scales covered in each issue, the magazine can encourage modellers to explore techniques & modelling themes that they would not previously have knowledge of.
